quran[13]{c,v,t}:
  72,1,"Maaku : "Wahayinaama e am, won'de dental jinna ke…óiimo [kam mi…óo jannga Alqur'aana], …ói wi'i: "Minen min nani janngeteende haawniinde."
  72,2,"Hende …óowira e peewal. Min ngooŇč…óinii nde. Min kafidatah e Joomi amen, hay e gooto."
  72,3,"E won'de manngural Joomi amen ngal mawnii, o siforaali jogitagol genndo, wonaa …ďi…ó…óo !"
  72,4,"E won'de [Ibuliisa] …óay…óo on e amen hino wowlaynoo penaale e hoore Allah."
  72,5,"Minen min cikkuno won'de yim…ďe e jinna wowlataano fenaande e hoore Allah."
  72,6,"Hari le wor…ďe yim…ďe hino mooloratnoo wor…ďe jinna, …ďe …ďesdi …ói bewre."
  72,7,"Kam…ďe [yim…ďe …ďeen] …ďe cikkir no sikkir…óon noon, won'de Allah immintintah hay gooto."
  72,8,"E won'de min meemii kammu ngun, min tawi hingu hebbiniraa aynoo…ďe tii…óu…ďe e docote."
  72,9,"E won'de mi…óen njoo…óotonoo ton fii ke…óagol. Kala non ke…óitii…óo jooni, o hawray e docotal tommbingal."
  72,10,"E won'de min nganndaa si ko bone fa'andanaa won…ďe ka leddi …ďen, kaa hara Joomi ma…ď…ďe faandani …ďe peewal."
  72,11,"E won'de hino e amen mo∆ī∆īu…ói, hino e amen kadi ko jaasi …óum. Hari mi…óen e laawi ceertu…ói."
  72,12,"E won'de min pellituno min laawotaako Allah ka hoore leydi, e won'de min laawortaa Mo dogugol."
  72,13,"E won'de nde min nanunoo peewal nagl, min ngoo…óini ngal. Kala gooŇč…óin…óo Joomi mum, oon hulataa …óuytaneede [mo∆ī∆īi] wonaa …ďeydaneede [bon…ói]."